庆祝 Maxi 的一生，无论您身在何处。如果您愿意捐款，Maxi 的愿望不是献花，而是向<a href="https://www.justgiving.com/fundraising/maxwell-fraser?fbclid=IwAR3DmmcXxQoSAV6D7jOmPBfrt3Rnobjq94GGDGY9DrAi3TnvtLHj_ag-ZIo">Centrepoint</a>捐款。 Centrepoint 是一家了不起的慈善机构，为英国的无家可归者提供住宿和支持。”</p><p>该乐队还宣布将于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/faithless-announce-return-to-the-stage-to-celebrate-maxi-jazz-at-camp-bestival-shropshire-2024-3580014">今年八月举办 Camp Bestival</a>演出 - 请<a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/camp-bestival-shropshire/?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=WyQS5CymqxyNU6mQdCxfu1IQUkHytnxEb0%3A5yc0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此</a>购买门票。他们还将出现在今年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/michael-kiwanuka-faithless-bicep-and-jessie-ware-lead-stacked-wilderness-2024-line-up-3594433">荒野节</a>上，您可以在<a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/wilderness-festival-tickets/artist/1562166?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=WyQS5CymqxyNU6mQdCxfu1IQUkHytiT8b0%3A5yc0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">这里</a>购买门票。</p><p>今天，格拉斯顿伯里的完整<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-line-up-revealed-who-playing-poster-3600775">阵容终于揭晓</a>。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dua-lipa">Dua Lipa</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/coldplay">Coldplay</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sza">SZA</a>将成为标志性金字塔舞台的主角，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shania-twain">Shania Twain</a>将填补周日的 Legends 席位。吐温称传奇老虎机为“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shania-twain-talks-glastonbury-2024-legends-slot-honour-of-my-life-3600979">我一生的荣幸</a>”，而利帕此前则称这个节日为“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dua-lipa-on-her-favourite-thing-about-glastonbury-3601162">我最喜欢、最喜欢的地方</a>”。</p><p>其他计划加入 Pyramid Stage 的乐队包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lcd-soundsystem">LCD Soundsystem</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/little-simz">Little Simz</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/burna-boy">Burna Boy</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pj-harvey">PJ Harvey</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cyndi-lauper">Cyndi Lauper</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/michael-kiwanuka">Michael Kiwanuka</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/janelle-monae">Janelle Monae</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/olivia-dean">Olivia Dean</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paloma-faith">Paloma Faith</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/keane">Keane</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/idles">Idles</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/disclosure">Disclosure</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-national">The National</a>预计将在其他舞台上名列前茅。其他乐队还有<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-streets">The Streets</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/two-door-cinema-club">Two Door Cinema Club</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/avril-lavigne">Avril Lavigne</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-last-dinner-party">The Last Evening Party</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jungle">Jungle</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/justice">Justice</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bloc-party">Bloc Party</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fontaines-d-c">Fontaines DC</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/yard-act">Yard Act</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/arlo-parks">Arlo Parks</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gossip">Gossip 等</a>。</p><p> 2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节将于 6 月 26 日星期三至 6 月 30 日星期日在萨默塞特皮尔顿的沃西农场举行。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-faithless-to-be-first-act-ever-to-headline-thursday-night-3601316">《格拉斯顿伯里 2024：Faithless 成为周四晚头条新闻》的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
